headlines.description: When he left the Colorado Rockies in the offseason, Michael Cuddyer was supposed to provide the New York Mets with a big bat in the middle of the lineup.
While Johnny Cueto's plan is to keep his focus on what he can control, Matt Boyd hopes to stick to the strategy that helped him to outpitch the ace last week.

video.headline: Tigers set to take on Royals

headlines.description: Chris Sale may need to be very good Monday night to end his team's free fall as well as his own.
